'''Busingye Kabumba''' (wavutse ku ya 12 Kamena 1982) ni umunyamategeko wa [[Ubugande|Uganda]] n'umusizi. Ni Umwarimu wamategeko, Ikigo cy’Uburenganzira bwa Muntu n’Amahoro (HURIPEC), mu ishami ry’amategeko, kaminuza ya Makerere akaba n’umufatanyabikorwa w’ubujyanama hamwe na M / S Law Law Associates.  Icyegeranyo cye cy’imivugo, "Kwongorera Ubugingo Bwanjye",  yatsindiye igihembo cya mbere mu cyiciro cy’imirimo yatangajwe mu gitabo cy’igihugu cy’ibitabo cy’igihugu cya Uganda (NABOTU) cyo mu 2002. Gusohora iki gitabo mu 2001 ubwo yari afite imyaka 19 y'amavuko byatumye aba umusizi muto wa Uganda wigeze gusohora icyegeranyo cyose cy'imivugo. 

== Ubuzima bwambere nuburere ==
Kabumba yavutse ku ya 21 Kamena 1982 na Porofeseri Ijuka Kabumba na Madamu Bazaire Kabumba, bombi bakaba ari abarimu. Ni uwa kane mu muryango w'abantu batanu. Yagiye mu ishuri ribanza rya St Kizito, Namilyango kaminuza ku rwego rwa "O" na King's College Budo ku rwego rwa "A".  Yarangije afite LL. B wo muri kaminuza ya Makerere . Busingye amaze kurangiza mu kigo gishinzwe iterambere ry'amategeko afite impamyabumenyi y'icyiciro cya kabiri cya kaminuza mu bijyanye n'amategeko mu by'amategeko, Busingye yize impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu by'amategeko mbonezamubano muri kaminuza ya Oxford . Nyuma yaje gukora ibijyanye n’amategeko muri kaminuza ya Harvard . 

